  <entry>
    <title>一些最近的AI工具整理</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/post/undefined.html"/>
    <id>http://example.com/post/undefined.html</id>
    <published>2022-12-08T06:33:33.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-12-08T09:36:09.554Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="美术"><a href="#美术" class="headerlink" title="美术"></a>美术</h2><h3 id="NovelAI"><a href="#NovelAI" class="headerlink" title="NovelAI"></a>NovelAI</h3><p>网址：<a href="https://novelai.net/">https://novelai.net/</a></p><p>前段时间比较火的模型，算是掀起ai作画浪潮的工具了</p><p><img src="/post/undefined/novelai.png" alt="NovelAI"></p><p>tips：贵，但是可以本地部署，b站一堆教程</p><h3 id="Midjourney"><a href="#Midjourney" class="headerlink" title="Midjourney"></a><strong>Midjourney</strong></h3><p>网址：<a href="https://midjourney.gitbook.io/docs/">快速入门指南 - 中途文档 (gitbook.io)</a></p><p>非常写实的画风</p><p>有时候能创作一些很震撼的图片</p><p><img src="/post/undefined/Midjourney_2.png"></p><p><img src="/post/undefined/Midjourney_1.png"></p><p>tips：需要使用discord，需要魔法，25次免费使用机会</p><h3 id="Stable-Diffusion"><a href="#Stable-Diffusion" class="headerlink" title="Stable Diffusion"></a><strong>Stable Diffusion</strong></h3><p>网址：<a href="https://stablediffusionweb.com/#demo">Stable Diffusion Online (stablediffusionweb.com)</a></p><p>写实，简单，开源，就是有点不够精致？会生成一些逆天的古神</p><p>比如：![](Stable Diffusion.png)</p><p>…..</p><p>反正有点跟不上时代了，但是easy to use。</p><h3 id="Clipasso"><a href="#Clipasso" class="headerlink" title="Clipasso"></a><strong>Clipasso</strong></h3><p>网址：<a href="https://clipasso.github.io/clipasso/">CLIPasso：语义感知对象草图</a></p><p>将图片转为简笔画，但…..</p><p><img src="/post/undefined/Clipasso.png"></p><p>很抽象</p><p>tips：开源，很慢</p><h3 id="文心大模型"><a href="#文心大模型" class="headerlink" title="文心大模型"></a>文心大模型</h3><p>网址：<a href="https://wenxin.baidu.com/ernie-vilg?curtype=exp">文心大模型 - 产业级知识增强大模型 (baidu.com)</a></p><p>百度的，可以一用</p><p><img src="/post/undefined/wenxing.png"></p><h2 id="代码"><a href="#代码" class="headerlink" title="代码"></a>代码</h2><h3 id="ChatGPT"><a href="#ChatGPT" class="headerlink" title="ChatGPT"></a>ChatGPT</h3><p>网址：<a href="https://openai.com/blog/chatgpt/">https://openai.com/blog/chatgpt/</a></p><p>神中神，这篇博客就是写给它的，copilot已经让我大开眼界了这玩意儿更是重量级。</p><p>目前最成熟的模型，和以前的智障完全不是一个东西，我用的时候给它带入成了传送门系列的G姐，总之多少有点聪明的吓人了。</p><p>ps：这网站之前被我弄坏了的时候就是通过它救回来的</p><p>多的不说，给大伙来点想看的东西：</p><p><img src="/post/undefined/chatgpt.png"></p><p><img src="/post/undefined/chatgpt1.png"></p><p>或者我向它提问：</p><p><img src="/post/undefined/chatgpt2.png"></p><p>这是它的回答：</p><figure class="highlight c#"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> UnityEngine;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">PlayerController</span> : <span class="title">MonoBehaviour</span></span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="built_in">float</span> moveSpeed = <span class="number">10.0f</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="built_in">float</span> jumpForce = <span class="number">10.0f</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="built_in">float</span> dashForce = <span class="number">10.0f</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> Rigidbody2D rb;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> <span class="built_in">bool</span> isGrounded = <span class="literal">false</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">Start</span>()</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        rb = GetComponent&lt;Rigidbody2D&gt;();</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">Update</span>()</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">// 移动</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">float</span> moveInput = Input.GetAxisRaw(<span class="string">&quot;Horizontal&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        rb.velocity = <span class="keyword">new</span> Vector2(moveInput * moveSpeed, rb.velocity.y);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">// 跳跃</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (Input.GetButtonDown(<span class="string">&quot;Jump&quot;</span>) &amp;&amp; isGrounded)</span><br><span class="line">        &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            rb.AddForce(<span class="keyword">new</span> Vector2(<span class="number">0</span>, jumpForce), ForceMode2D.Impulse);</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">// 冲刺</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (Input.GetButtonDown(<span class="string">&quot;Dash&quot;</span>))</span><br><span class="line">        &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            rb.AddForce(<span class="keyword">new</span> Vector2(dashForce, <span class="number">0</span>), ForceMode2D.Impulse);</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">OnCollisionEnter2D</span>(<span class="params">Collision2D collision</span>)</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (collision.gameObject.tag == <span class="string">&quot;Ground&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            isGrounded = <span class="literal">true</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">OnCollisionExit2D</span>(<span class="params">Collision2D collision</span>)</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (collision.gameObject.tag == <span class="string">&quot;Ground&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            isGrounded = <span class="literal">false</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/post/undefined/chatgpt3.png"></p><p>毫无疑问是一个标准的答案，然而它的功能远比这个强大，这只是一个非常基础的问题，我更看好他在计算机图形学上的前景。</p><p>tips：对方ban了国服和一些地区，要使用最好是挂美国日本等地区的代理，hktw这些也不行，注册账号需要外国的电话号码收验证码（虚拟电话不行），可以使用接码平台问题不是很大。</p><h3 id="Copilot"><a href="#Copilot" class="headerlink" title="Copilot"></a>Copilot</h3><p>网站：<a href="https://github.com/features/copilot">https://github.com/features/copilot</a></p><p>装vscode上自己写代码的时候会有提醒，专业程度比不上上面那位，但是更方便使用，且有代码自动补全的功能</p><p>当时有这玩意儿的时候大伙说这会砸了饭碗，然而现在…..</p><p><img src="/post/undefined/copilot.png"></p><p>图中灰色部分代码即为自动补全的提示代码，只是简单的帮我写了下状态机，当然也可以像chatgpt一样帮你把函数写完。</p><p>用来当辅助使用还行</p><p>tips：要钱，学生免费，新人有两个月试用期</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
